OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,FNational Highways staff switch on the
OL,8,Fclosed lane signs when stopped
OL,9,Fvehicles are detected in live lanes to
OL,10,Fprevent them being hit from behind and
OL,11,Fto help and protect the emergency
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FSince September 2022, all police
OL,15,Fforces have been able to use
OL,16,Fenforcement cameras to prosecute
OL,17,Fmotorists who illegally pass under a
OL,18,Fred X or enter a lane beyond one of
OL,19,Fthe signs.
