OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,FThis can result in a fine of up to
OL,8,F#100 and three penalty points, or more
OL,9,Fsevere penalties and a court
OL,10,Fappearance in some cases.
OL,12,FFigures obtained by IAM RoadSmart
OL,13,Ffollowing Freedom of Information
OL,14,Frequests to police forces revealed
OL,15,F4,393 incidents were recorded in 2021,
OL,16,Frising to 20,773 in 2022 and 28,231 in
OL,17,F2023.
