OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,FBetween 2021-23 inclusive, Surrey
OL,8,FPolice topped the table with 11,360
OL,9,Fdrivers caught committing Red X
OL,10,Foffences along stretches of the M3,
OL,11,FM23 and M25 ` the latter being
OL,12,FBritain's busiest motorway.
OL,14,FThames Valley Police had the second
OL,15,Fhighest volume with 9,957 motorists
OL,16,Fbeing snapped by cameras over the same
OL,17,Fperiod.
