OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,FMeera Naran, whose eight-year-old son
OL,8,FDev died in a smart motorway crash on
OL,9,Fthe M6 near Birmingham in May 2018,
OL,10,Fsaid: "In an emergency, every second
OL,11,Fcounts.
OL,13,F"The red X provides a layer of safety
OL,14,Ffor the public, emergency services,
OL,15,Frecovery operators and road workers.
OL,17,F"An incident can occur on any lane of
OL,18,Fthe motorway and lanes are closed for
OL,19,Fa number of reasons.
