OL,3,CMore than 53,000 incidents of drivers
OL,4,Cignoring smart motorway lane closed
OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,F"When in operation and abided by, this
OL,8,Fcould save a number of lives,
OL,9,Fincluding your own."
OL,11,FIAM RoadSmart director of policy and
OL,12,Fstandards Nicholas Lyes said:
OL,13,F"Ignoring a red X sign on a smart
OL,14,Fmotorway is dangerous because it risks
OL,15,Fa serious collision and, for this
OL,16,Freason, we welcome police forces
OL,17,Fclamping down on those who break the
OL,18,Flaw.
