OL,3,CMore than 53,000 incidents of drivers
OL,4,Cignoring smart motorway lane closed
OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,F"The majority of drivers have serious
OL,8,Freservations about the safety of smart
OL,9,Fmotorways where the hard shoulder has
OL,10,Fbeen removed, and these figures are
OL,11,Funlikely to persuade them they are
OL,12,Fsafe.
OL,14,F"We know that no new all-lane running
OL,15,Fsmart motorways will be built but it
OL,16,Fdoes beg the question of what we do
OL,17,Fwith the existing stretches that are
OL,18,Fin operation?
OL,20,F"This is something the new Government
OL,21,Fneeds to give some serious thought to."
