OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,FSmart motorways without a hard
OL,8,Fshoulder were created to increase
OL,9,Fcapacity at a lower cost than widening
OL,10,Froads.
OL,12,FThen-prime minister Rishi Sunak
OL,13,Fcancelled all future planned smart
OL,14,Fmotorway projects in April last year,
OL,15,Fciting financial pressures and a lack
OL,16,Fof public confidence in the roads.
OL,18,FThis led to calls for the hard
OL,19,Fshoulder to be reinstated on existing
OL,20,Fsmart motorways.
