OL,7,FA National Highways spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"ARed X signal is there to increase
OL,9,Fthe safety of everyone using the road
OL,10,Fby highlighting an issue ahead.
OL,12,F"Above 90% of drivers observe Red X
OL,13,Fsignals, but ignoring Red X signals is
OL,14,Fan offence and puts themselves and
OL,15,Fothers at risk."
